A towering medieval castle gate with an enormous ornate iron lock mechanism at its center, rendered in Studio Ghibli animation style with soft watercolor textures and warm sunset lighting. The gate protects a fantastical walled garden filled with floating geometric crystal structures representing code modules. Vines with glowing leaves climb the ancient stone walls, while small mechanical brass keys of various sizes float in the air around the lock, each key slightly different in design. The atmosphere is mystical yet protective, with golden hour light casting long shadows across cobblestone ground. Fluffy clouds drift in a peachy-orange sky above the fortress walls, and tiny fireflies begin to emerge in the dimming light.
